peter fisher ( born 29 march 1954 ) is an australian film and television actor who was most active in the period from the mid-1970s to the late-1990s .   in the early 1990s he started to move into the area of corporate communications .   in 1995 he created " act one ! "   ( act one theatre based learning pty ltd ) in sydney , a company that specialises in corporate training and development .   in the early 2000s he became involved with the university of new south wales ' australian graduate school of management , particularly the middle manager program born in katoomba , new south wales , he studied architecture at sydney university , graduating in 1974 .